            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-2-1634037997500-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Meanwhile, peel and finely chop (or grate) the <strong>garlic</strong></p><p>Combine the <strong>chopped garlic</strong> (not a big garlic fan? Try using less!), <strong>tahini</strong>, <strong>mayo </strong>and <strong>rice vinegar</strong> in a large bowl – this is your <strong>Japanese-style dressing</strong></p>",
